# Environment Variables for TTISA NTUT Website

## For Development (.env.local)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

## For Production (Vercel Environment Variables)
# Set these in your Vercel dashboard:
# 1. Go to your project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Settings > Environment Variables
# 3. Add these variables:

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

## Supabase Auth Configuration
# Make sure to configure these URLs in your Supabase project:
# 1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Authentication > URL Configuration
# 2. Add these URLs to "Site URL" and "Redirect URLs":

# Site URL: https://ttisa-ntut.vercel.app
# Redirect URLs:
# - https://ttisa-ntut.vercel.app
# - https://ttisa-ntut.vercel.app/auth/callback
# - https://ttisa-ntut.vercel.app/update-password
# - http://localhost:5173 (for development)
# - http://localhost:5173/auth/callback (for development)
# - http://localhost:5173/update-password (for development)